nodes.text: I personally have suffered from peanut allergies for over 40 years.
kateinhawaii(579): I personally have suffered from peanut allergies for over 40 years.
Annot: I personally have suffered from peanut allergies for over 40 years.
If there are packaged peanuts served on board a flight, it's 100% guaranteed that I will have a reaction from the peanut dust.
kateinhawaii(579): If there are packaged peanuts served on board a flight, it's 100% guaranteed that I will have a reaction from the peanut dust.
Annot: If there are packaged peanuts served on board a flight, it's 100% guaranteed that I will have a reaction from the peanut dust.
I do not agree with a buffer zone for a couple of reasons.
kateinhawaii(579): I do not agree with a buffer zone for a couple of reasons.
Annot: I do not agree with a buffer zone for a couple of reasons.
For me, it's the dust in the air.
kateinhawaii(579): For me, it's the dust in the air.
Annot: For me, it's the dust in the air.
Someone posted that the air circulates peanut dust right out of the air
kateinhawaii(579): Someone posted that the air circulates peanut dust right out of the air
Annot: Someone posted that the air circulates peanut dust right out of the air
but apparently not quick enough to prevent a life threatening reaction.
kateinhawaii(579): but apparently not quick enough to prevent a life threatening reaction.
Annot: but apparently not quick enough to prevent a life threatening reaction.
You know, airlines tried to create nonsmoking zones on airplanes but that didn't work either.
kateinhawaii(579): You know, airlines tried to create nonsmoking zones on airplanes but that didn't work either.
Annot: You know, airlines tried to create nonsmoking zones on airplanes but that didn't work either.
I have been on flights where nasty (and do I mean NASTY) flight attendants have made sarcastic remarks about me and my allergies especially on one Delta flight.
kateinhawaii(579): I have been on flights where nasty (and do I mean NASTY) flight attendants have made sarcastic remarks about me and my allergies especially on one Delta flight.
Annot: I have been on flights where nasty (and do I mean NASTY) flight attendants have made sarcastic remarks about me and my allergies especially on one Delta flight.
Northwest was great
kateinhawaii(579): Northwest was great
Annot: Northwest was great
because they respected their passengers enough to address their concerns
kateinhawaii(579): because they respected their passengers enough to address their concerns
Annot: because they respected their passengers enough to address their concerns
and prohibited peanuts altogether.
kateinhawaii(579): and prohibited peanuts altogether.
Annot: and prohibited peanuts altogether.
It was as much a relief to walk onto one of their flights as it was to walk onto one of the first smoke free flights!
kateinhawaii(579): It was as much a relief to walk onto one of their flights as it was to walk onto one of the first smoke free flights!
Annot: It was as much a relief to walk onto one of their flights as it was to walk onto one of the first smoke free flights!
Smokers use to use the same logic and reasoning to justify smoking on flights as these peanut proponents are using now.
kateinhawaii(579): Smokers use to use the same logic and reasoning to justify smoking on flights as these peanut proponents are using now.
Annot: Smokers use to use the same logic and reasoning to justify smoking on flights as these peanut proponents are using now.
I flew on many smoking flights and never needed to inject myself so that I could breathe
kateinhawaii(579): I flew on many smoking flights and never needed to inject myself so that I could breathe
Annot: I flew on many smoking flights and never needed to inject myself so that I could breathe
I can't say the same for flights with peanuts.
kateinhawaii(579): I can't say the same for flights with peanuts.
Annot: I can't say the same for flights with peanuts.
The airline industry can not be left to selfmonitor this.
Antanagoge(598): The airline industry can not be left to selfmonitor this.
Annot: The airline industry can not be left to selfmonitor this.
Studies have shown that the quality of information from airline customer service department is highly variable and, in some cases, incomplete or inaccurate.

Annot: Studies have shown that the quality of information from airline customer service department is highly variable and, in some cases, incomplete or inaccurate.
The psychological effects of this, combined with the risk of death, are significant.
Antanagoge(598): The psychological effects of this, combined with the risk of death, are significant.
Annot: The psychological effects of this, combined with the risk of death, are significant.
